snippet.title: He Got Voted Out For His Laugh - Among Us
snippet.description:
THIS IS OUR 50TH AMONG US VIDEO! 

Please considering subscribing to the channel if you enjoy these! We love making them. Shoutout to Kush (our editor) and Nyx (our thumbnail artist) for absolutely destroying it this past year.

The Scientist can check vitals at any time. The engineer can vent. The Guardian Angel (must be dead for this role) can offer a shield to prevent crewmates from dying. The Shapeshifter role allows impostors to disguise themselves as crewmates more easily. #AmongUs

Everyone was an engineer which was completely chaotic.
